<statement>
<p>
A population of bacteria is growing according to the equation <m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={2000}{e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m>.  Estimate when the population will exceed 6925.</p>
<p>
<em>t</em>= <input type="text" style="width:25ch" name="qn0" id="qn0" value="" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Question 1" class="text"/> Â  </p>
<p>
