</p>
</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>6.8999492861859</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={2000}{e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{6925}={2000}{e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{6925}}{{2000}}={e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{6925}}{{2000}}\right)}}}={0.18}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{6925}}{{2000}}\right)}}}}{{0.18}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={6.8999492861859}</m></p>
</solution>
